{"tid":1348742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世文宣] share元朗資料之前大家要記得宣揚班狗，政府，黑社會同中共既衰野落去","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:52:36.000Z","uid":89974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b02abee10781d90988d86d2192572d88ce424b74","tid":1348742,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共</span></span>：為咗打壓人民而指示黑社會出嚟做野，叫班狗唔准出手，結果尋晚元朗班無辜市民差啲俾人殺哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">政府</span></span>：想籍黑社會嚟樹立班狗既威嚴，重建更兇殘既軍政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">狗</span></span>：完全無視市民生命安全，999打唔通，班狗同黑社會有傾有講，放哂人走，兇番受害者，人都拉唔到個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑社會</span>：隨便打人唔駛負責任，同班狗一齊狼狽為奸，今日我地唔阻止佢，第日18區既黑社會全部走哂出嚟話事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講清講楚係呢四個團體想殺香港人，植入俾和理非同中立派既意識入面</span></span>"},{"pid":"5dcaa173860e7efab626f72ccac05d0414d5b08f","tid":1348742,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d288bf436cf644bc13543e8629581e4cd89df75","tid":1348742,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca58eff34f2ae4a99a37607d6f222bb295d728e2","tid":1348742,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}